videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson tries to make the cross-court pass, but it goes flying over his teammate's head and into the crowd.
videos.headline: Markell Johnson a little high on the pass

videos.description: NC State's Devon Daniels gets the defender up in the air and is able to knock down the 3-pointer at the end of the shot clock.
videos.headline: Daniels pump fakes, knocks down the 3

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Nickeil Alexander-Walker gets the dribble hand off and goes right down the lane for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Alexander-Walker flushes two-handed jam
